      "Text": "Security update for grub2",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for grub2 fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2020-15705: Fail kernel validation without shim protocol (bsc#1174421).\n- Add fibre channel device's ofpath support to grub-ofpathname and search hint to speed up root device discovery (bsc#1172745).\n\nThis update was imported from the SUSE:SLE-15-SP1:Update update project.",
